@startuml
!include style.puml
skinparam arrowThickness 1.1
skinparam arrowColor MODEL_COLOR
skinparam classBackgroundColor MODEL_COLOR

Package Model <<Rectangle>>{
Interface ReadOnlyTrack2Gather <<Interface>>
Interface ReadOnlyUserPrefs <<Interface>>
Interface Model <<Interface>>
Class Track2Gather
Class ReadOnlyTrack2Gather
Class Model
Class ModelManager
Class UserPrefs
Class ReadOnlyUserPrefs


Class UniquePersonList
Class Person
Class Name
Class Phone
Class Email
Class CaseNumber
Class Address
Class WorkAddress
Class QuarantineAddress
Class ShnPeriod
Class NextOfKinName
Class NextOfKinPhone
Class NextOfKinAddress
Class CallStatus

}

Class HiddenOutside #FFFFFF
HiddenOutside ..> Model

Track2Gather .up.|> ReadOnlyTrack2Gather

ModelManager .up.|> Model
Model .right.> ReadOnlyUserPrefs
Model .left.> ReadOnlyTrack2Gather
ModelManager -left-> "1" Track2Gather
ModelManager -right-> "1" UserPrefs
UserPrefs .up.|> ReadOnlyUserPrefs

Track2Gather *--> "1" UniquePersonList
UniquePersonList --> "~* all" Person
Person *--> Name
Person *--> Phone
Person *--> Email
Person *--> CaseNumber
Person *--> Address
Person *--> "0..1" WorkAddress
Person *--> "0..1" QuarantineAddress
Person *--> "0..1" ShnPeriod
Person *--> "0..1" NextOfKinName
Person *--> "0..1" NextOfKinPhone
Person *--> "0..1" NextOfKinAddress
Person *--> CallStatus

Address -[hidden]right-> Name
Name -[hidden]right-> Phone

WorkAddress -[hidden]right-> QuarantineAddress
QuarantineAddress -[hidden]right-> NextOfKinAddress
NextOfKinAddress -[hidden]right-> NextOfKinName
NextOfKinName -[hidden]right-> NextOfKinPhone
NextOfKinPhone -[hidden]right-> Email
Email -[hidden]right-> CaseNumber
CaseNumber -[hidden]right-> ShnPeriod
ShnPeriod -[hidden]right-> CallStatus

WorkAddress ..> Address
QuarantineAddress ..> Address
NextOfKinName ..> Name
NextOfKinPhone ..> Phone
NextOfKinAddress ..> Address

ModelManager -->"~* filtered" Person
@enduml
